er"><span class="post_detail_date">April 9, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/charliehuston/">Charlie Huston</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/ian-fleming-special-correspondent-to-a-moscow-show-trial/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/04/fleming2-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/ian-fleming-special-correspondent-to-a-moscow-show-trial/">Ian Fleming, Special Correspondent to a Moscow Show Trial</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">April 9, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/nicholasshakespeare/">Nicholas Shakespeare</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/the-true-crime-writers-favorite-true-crime/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2018/12/library-books-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/the-true-crime-writers-favorite-true-crime/">The True Crime Writer's Favorite True Crime</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">April 9, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/philipeil/">Philip Eil</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
